title: Le Sud
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegetarian and fish. Little deli-type shop on the Haarlemmerdijk, next door to the Bagels & Beans. Offers a range of foods including sandwiches (aubergine, falafel, or hummus) served on Turkish bread, many varieties of hummus, other vegetarian (mostly vegan) dishes. A few dishes do contain milk or cheese.
